<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte.Ltd.</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />2 Loyang Crescent</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />508976 Singapore</span></div>
<div class="WordSection1">
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">June 29, 2015<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Qatar Airways, </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">As a follow up to our letter dated April 14<sup>th</sup>, we would like to assure you that Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd. (Avionics R&amp;O Site at Loyang site), is progressing with the <span style="color: black;">transition to the Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) organization. This change will simplify the way in which you conduct business with Honeywell and deliver a more efficient and effective procurement experience.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">As an extension of the existing business environment and structure, the business activity currently linked with the Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd facility (Avionics R&amp;O Site at Loyang site), will transition to Honeywell International S&agrave;rl, currently targeted for October 2015. </span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">We appreciate your understanding and cooperation for a seamless transition for you and your organization. As a reminder, here are the steps you will need to take:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Update your Authorized Supplier List (ASL) and internal systems to reflect the new Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) legal entity. <br /><br /> </span> 
<ul>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The new supplier address for the Singapore Loyang procurement and accounting transactions is:<br /> <br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Honeywell International S&agrave;rl<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Aerospace R&amp;O<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; Z.A. La Pi&egrave;ce 16,<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 1180 Rolle, Switzerland<br /> <br /> </span></li>
<li><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">The amended &ldquo;Ship To&rdquo; address for the Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Avionics R&amp;O site is:<br /> <br />&nbsp;&nbsp; Honeywell International S&agrave;rl<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; C/O Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd.,<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 2 Loyang Crescent<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp; 508976 Singapore<br /><br /></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: black;">Execute a Novation Agreement to assign rights and obligations from Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd. to </span>Honeywell International S&agrave;rl. <span style="color: windowtext;">Our Contracts team has been in contact with your company to provide additional information to complete this</span><span style="color: windowtext;"> action.</span> </span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: windowtext;">As we go through this transition, we want to assure you that we have your best interests in mind and we will provide additional details 60, 30 and 5 days prior to October 2015. </span><span style="color: black;">We have also attached a <a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore FAQs 06.27.2015.pdf">frequently asked questions</a> document on this transition.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: windowtext; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">For your information, concurrently as a separate project, we are enhancing the SAP software at other R&amp;O sites in August and October 2015. The August transition will include sites in Tempe, Arizona; Wichita, Kansas; Basingstoke, UK, and Shanghai, China. The October transition will include sites in Renton, Washington; Rocky Mount, North Carolina; Toulouse, France, and Tucson, Arizona. We are providing updates to our customers who conduct business at these sites.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact your Honeywell Customer Business Manager. <br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Yours Sincerely,</span></p>
</div>
